<div style="font-size:90%">
<br>

<div style="color:#4B4B4B;">	



We cordially invite all aikidoists and prospective aikido students to train with us at the annual seminar jointly organized by Aikido Philippines (AP), the Filipino Federation of Aikido (FFA), and the Pilipinas Aikido Propagation Association (PAPA).<br><br>

Hiroshi Fujimaki Shihan, 7th dan, of Japan Aikikai, shall lead the seminar.<br><br>

The two-day seminar shall be on 2019 November 30 - December 01 (Saturday-Sunday), at the Copeland Covered Courts, UP Los Baños campus, Los Baños, Laguna.<br><br>

Details are in the accompanying poster.<br><br>

A traditional farewell dinner will be held on the evening of December 1st. Everyone is welcome to this dinner. Venue TBA.<br><br>

For full details on seminar contribution amounts, schedules, venue location map, mechanics of contribution remittance, and others, please visit the Home page of <a href="http://www.makatiaikidoclub.com" target="_blank"><font color="blue"><b><i><u>www.makatiaikidoclub.com</u></i></b></font></a> and click on the image of the poster for the event that will be prominent on that page.<br><br>

We hope to see you there.<br><br><br>


Sincerely,<br><br>

Cris Buenaseda, Aikido Philippines<br>
Rommel Miel, Aikido Philippines<br>
Carlos Hubilla, Pilipinas Aikido Propagation Association<br>
Victor Ayes, Pilipinas Aikido Propagation Association<br>
Marielle Macapawa, Kannagara Davao Dojo/Filipino Federation of Aikido<br>
Dam Amaranto, Makati Aikido Club/Filipino Federation of Aikido<br>
Royce Reyes, Makati Aikido Club/Filipino Federation of Aikido<br><br><br><br>

